review_title: Tea box came with liquid stain.
reviews: Ordered 2 boxes of this tea. It came today, package is dry and intact. When I open it, I noticed that one of the box had a liquid stain on it or kinda got wet at one point. I have no idea what it is but it smells a little bit fishy. Unfortunately, when I open the box to see the tea bags inside, it is also got stained. What a waste.
Smoke it if you got it!
Looks the same going in as it does on the way out, 5 Stars!

Best investment ever for -40 deg Fort McMurray winters. Just get it.
I used the purple one for my Rolex band. Worked perfectly.
Better than the Corsair mousepad! For those OCD folks - It's nice that the logo can be turned any direction without being upside down.

I suppose this unit is great for those that have nothing else connected to their TV. I on the other hand, have a high end gaming laptop connected to mine. Should have trusted my gut and not bought this, since using this doesn't even come close to being as good as my current setup. Should have known better.

I'll eventually move this down to the basement TV if I can ever get my NAS mounted on this bloody thing.......
I only leave negative reviews. But, this mouse was just so good that I had to leave a comment. Simply the best.

Got the RGB mat and it does not lay flat. Tried everything. This mat is Aladdins magic carpet with a mind of its own.

Pretty disappointed, returned for refund. Going to try a knock-off, "make America great again" version that hopefully doesnt fall apart after a week and sits flat on the desk.
